headline: Clorox Pre-Q4 Earnings Send Mixed Signals: Time to Accumulate Shares?
summary: CLX's Q4 performance is likely to have benefited from margin strength and innovation, but macro headwinds and rising costs keep investors cautious.

headline: P&G beats on earnings, warns of $1 billion tariff hit
summary: P&G said it will see a $1 billion hit to profits in its new fiscal year as a result of tariffs and offered mixed earnings-per-share guidance as a result.
